            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本第二大銀行計畫在債市暴跌告一段落後大舉買入日本國債",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CM5Mv.HXacXlVKXiM_qr_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e92ffda2c57138f8ab93a54c1d01ff34\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本第二大銀行<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:三井住友金融集團;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/三井住友金融集團\">三井住友金融集團</a>計畫在這輪日債殖利率劇烈飆升告一段落後，大舉買入日本國債。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三井住友金融集團全球市場主管永田有広在接受採訪時表示，一旦完成全面建倉，該集團的日本國債投資組合規模有望達到目前10.6萬億日圓（約670億美元）的兩倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本國債價格周二暴跌，長債殖利率升至歷史新高，投資者在選舉臨近之際日益擔憂首相高市早苗的財政政策。過去幾年，隨著日本央行逐步退出大規模購債計畫，殖利率一路走高，這引發市場猜測銀行等大型機構何時會重返日本國債市場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e706d0cb-98fa-34cf-8d32-24c811c3d57c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"永田有広攝影師：Akio Kon/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q8GRzTXQFsHOE4Z__9opoQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3ac7aa1986faa3c5ba4527f892a881ec\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">永田有広攝影師：Akio Kon/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我以前一直青睞海外債券，但今非昔比，現在關注日本國債，」永田有広說。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">永田有広在一場內容廣泛的採訪中還對日本市場作出了一些頗為引人注目的預測，包括未來幾年美元/日圓可能觸及180，以及今年底日經225指數有望從目前不到53,000點升破60,000點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他預計日本10年期國債殖利率將在今年底升破2.5%，並認為其合理區間在2.5%至3%。東京時間周三中午時分，日本10年期國債殖利率約為2.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">永田有広表示，三井住友已在買入一些30年期日本國債，並補充說，這類債券價格在本周初就已接近合理水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NWaqxAk3Aab2ThGrQU9z_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/104aac53953b3cc2c1ee56c5e962d4c4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Second-Largest Bank Plans Big JGB Purchases After Rout</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%9C%A8%E5%82%B5%E5%B8%82%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%E5%91%8A-%E6%AE%B5%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%89%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5-043054739.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 13:25:42",
